Quantix is currently hiring CDL-A tanker truck drivers for our liquid & dry bulk divisions.

•	Home often – out & back lanes
•	Top earners can make more than $100,000 per year

•	Paid vacation
•	$6,000 referral bonus program
•	Safety inspection bonus
•	Full benefits
•	9 paid company holidays

CDL-A Truck Driver Requirements:

• 1 year tractor/trailer experience
• Valid Class A CDL
• TWIC required
